flowchart TD
    %% Invoice Lifecycle State Machine Flow
    %% Generated by: GitHub Copilot – Claude Sonnet 4.6

    START([Invoice Created]) --> PENDING

    PENDING[PENDING\nAwaiting Approval]
    APPROVED[APPROVED\nEligible for Payment]
    REJECTED([REJECTED\nTerminal])
    SCHEDULED[SCHEDULED\nPayment Planned]
    PAID([PAID\nTerminal])
    CANCELLED([CANCELLED\nTerminal])

    PENDING -->|approve\nactor: MANAGER\nBR-004| APPROVED
    PENDING -->|reject\nactor: MANAGER\nreason required\nBR-004| REJECTED
    PENDING -->|cancel\nactor: ANALYST / MANAGER| CANCELLED

    APPROVED -->|schedule_payment\nactor: TREASURER\nscheduled_date required\nBR-006, BR-007| SCHEDULED
    APPROVED -->|cancel\nactor: MANAGER| CANCELLED

    SCHEDULED -->|payment_confirmed\nactor: SYSTEM\nbanking webhook| PAID
    SCHEDULED -->|cancel\nactor: MANAGER\npayment not yet sent| CANCELLED

    style PENDING fill:#FFF3CD,stroke:#856404,color:#856404
    style APPROVED fill:#D1E7DD,stroke:#0F5132,color:#0F5132
    style SCHEDULED fill:#CFE2FF,stroke:#084298,color:#084298
    style REJECTED fill:#F8D7DA,stroke:#842029,color:#842029
    style PAID fill:#D1E7DD,stroke:#0F5132,color:#0F5132
    style CANCELLED fill:#E2E3E5,stroke:#41464B,color:#41464B
    style START fill:#6C757D,color:#fff
